Package: flovenet
Version: 0.1.0
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Essential: no
Maintainer: Flovenet Team <dev@flovenet.io>
Homepage: https://flovenet.io
Description: Decentralized compute sharing network
 Flovenet is a P2P network for sharing computing resources
 (CPU, RAM, GPU, storage) across devices. It supports WASM
 job execution, social features, and a reputation system.
 .
 This package installs the flovenet daemon and API gateway,
 along with systemd service files for automatic startup.
Depends: libssl3, ca-certificates, libc6 (>= 2.31)
